dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Fixed 4 multipart sliver errors. 2. Fixed 26 gap errors and 2 overlap errors. 3. Admin1 name "TirisZemmour" was given a space. 4. Created and populated reference name field. 5. Fixed leading space errors in 8 Admin2 names. 6. Fixed 6 missing space errors in Admin2 names. 7. Fixed Admin2 name "0". Correct name is "Maal".
